result.name: Unity Ramen

reviews.text: Ramen was not  that bad need to que up for a bit dumplings was great i recommend it bit pricey but taste good

Quite unique ramen bar in Tsuen wan, you need to buy tickets outside the shop which feels like any of the ramen bar in Japan. They served great varieties of ramen particular the Alaskan king crab one, the soup base and ingredients are good! But the texture of ramen need to improve.

Interesting try for the buying machine in HK. Though it is not 100% the same as the machine in Japanese. Much appreciated!  Taste of the ramen is not bad, but you would find a bit better ramen in Tsuen Wan. Texture of the straigh noodle is much closer to the Japanese one.
good noodles, ok pork.

The way of purchasing is really like Japanese style. Heard of this ramen place online and thought would give it a try. Not a fan of the machine actually but seems like it is what make this place different. 
Ordered the garlic ramen. It was really just average. Didn't have a strong smell when it came and even after I tasted, just as expected. The broth was not rich or special. It was a garlic ramen but couldn't really taste the garlic flavor. Allegedly has 3 kinds of garlic but unfortunately none was good. The egg was just blend. The pork was just too much fat. Noodle was okay. But just everything else was a disappointment. The smell of the sakura shrimp ramen seemed nice though but didn't try. But wouldn't expect much after eating my garlic ramen. 
Also, there is no extra seasoning or garlic provided on the table. Was a bit disappointed about that. I feel like putting garlic in other ramen places makes a better garlic ramen than this.
Won't be trying again. A good ramen place is just hard to find.

result.name: 團日式拉麵

reviews.text: 香港食拉麵要撳都喺第一次，至於拉麵🍜可以拍得住日本🇯🇵地道口味，真喺唔錯好好味
叫了黑蒜油拉麵，麵口感煙韌，叉燒肉質柔軟不是厚肉質那種，但是調味很好，湯底不咸，非常喜歡！幾乎飲完整碗湯，我認為這裡較適合女士胃口，男士可能要選加麵才夠飽，會再光顧！
第一次係香港食拉麵用自助售票機，幾得意。湯底夠濃，拉麵份量足夠。每碗拉麵都有火灸叉燒，薄切，本人幾鍾意🤤 舖位不算大，有二十幾個位。
100%日本風味，推介魚介曲拉麵！
Ramen was not  that bad need to que up for a bit dumplings was great i recommend it bit pricey but taste good
